        <text x="950" y="151" fill="#6d6962" font-family="'JetBrains Mono Variable', monospace" font-size="11">now running on</text>
        <text x="950" y="169" fill="#6d6962" font-family="'JetBrains Mono Variable', monospace" font-size="11">other orgs.</text>
