    <p class="close-thesis rv d1">Make the invisible <em>legible</em>.</p>
    <p class="lede rv d2" style="max-width:58ch">An organization that can be read can be understood — by its people, and by the AI meant to help them. We've built the method, run it end to end, and proven the engines. <strong>The hard part is done.</strong> What's missing is the surface that puts it in anyone's hands — and that's the thing worth building.</p>
